==English==
===Adverb===
'''notwithstanding'''
# [[nevertheless]], [[all the same]]
===Conjunction===
'''notwithstanding'''
# [[although]]
===Preposition===
'''notwithstanding'''
# [[in spite of]], used postpositionally many times.
#: '''''Notwithstanding''' the re-election of Mrs Thatcher in 1983 and 1987, a clear majority of voters have favoured increased taxes.''
#: ''That caveat '''notwithstanding''', those close to Mr Bush insist that there was an effort to get a non-military solution.''

